            li
              em Your ability to Access, Update and Correct Personal Information.
              |  We maintain a procedure in order to help you confirm that your Personal Information remains correct and up-to-date. At any time, you may visit your personal profile at [www.imagewiki.org]. Through your personal profile you may review and update your Personal Information that we have already collected.
